    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到\"解决或关闭\"，这里是否包含无效事件的情况？比如误报或垃圾信息，是否需要单独的拒绝路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rejected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，需要加上Rejected状态。Open状态应该可以直接拒绝，标注为\"无效/垃圾信息\"。同时Open到InReview的触发条件是\"操作员确认\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Open",
        "Rejected",
        "InReview"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建主干结构：起始点到Open，Open分出两条线——到InReview（操作员确认）和到Rejected（无效/垃圾）。InReview再分解决和升级两条路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Open",
        "InReview",
        "Rejected",
        "Resolved",
        "Escalated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "InReview到Resolved的条件是\"问题已清除/验证修复\"，到Escalated则是\"严重或需要权限操作\"。另外Escalated解决后也要到Resolved，标注\"操作完成\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InReview",
        "Resolved",
        "Escalated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已补充这些迁移条件。现在Resolved和Rejected都是终态，需要连接到终止节点。Open的显示名称我设为\"新建事件已上报\"，这样更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Resolved",
        "Rejected",
        "[*]",
        "Open"
